songs.lyrics:
[Intro: DJ Cipha Sounds]
You see, what we have here, is a failure to communicate
My name is DJ Cipha Sounds, big dog Pitbull, Star Trak
And I'm here to explain a very serious problem
My man Fam-Lay out of Virginia
Down with The Neptunes, Star Trak, Def Jam
It's a no lose situation, it's like money in the bank
I'm not even doing a lot of talking
I'mma let my man Fam-Lay explain to you, what he does
Why we have a very serious problem
songs.title: Intro
